<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.6.4">
<l>ciramu ṉaintu maintuñ cintac ceṉṟarakkaṉ</l>
<l>uramuṅ karamun tuṇitta vuravō ṉūrpōlum</l>
<l>iravum pakalu mīṉtēṉ murala maṉṟellām</l>
<l>kuraviṉ pūvē tāṉma ṇamnāṟuṅ kuṟuṅkuṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kuṟuṅkuṭi, where the fragrance of bottle flower blossoms</l>
<l>Scents all of the courtyards, as honeybees hum there day and night,</l>
<l>Is like the city of the strong one who severed [both] the hands and chest</l>
<l>Of the demon, having first gone to scatter [his] five-and-five heads.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
